data.description: You'll love this house and all it has to offer. The views from the family room and lanai are priceless. This house has water views with preserve and no rear neighbors at all. Spacious layout of the house allows for a living room, dining room, kitchen and family room areas. Bedrooms are a great size and have ample closet space. Bedrooms could also serve as an office space. Newly added tile floors through out the bedrooms. Tile throughout the entire house. Newly painted interior walls, doors and baseboards. House is wired for an alarm system. Family room and primary suite wired for surround sound. Upgraded USB outlet in kitchen for electronics.   This is a great house for any family or couple. HOA dues are low. No CDD fees. Gated neighborhood. Access from 69th street, main entrance, also access to neighborhood through Oak Leaf Hammock on Mendoza road.
